sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Producer
    participant SM as Shared Memory
    participant C as Consumer

    Note over P,C: Initialization Phase
    P->>SM: openSharedBuffer(create=true)
    C->>SM: openSharedBuffer(create=false)
    
    Note over P,C: Initial Sync
    C->>SM: read_idx = 0
    C->>SM: futex_wait(write_idx)
    P->>SM: Check read_idx = 0
    Note over P: Write to buffer[0]
    P->>SM: write_idx = 0
    P->>SM: futex_wake(write_idx)
    
    Note over P,C: First Consumer Cycle
    Note over P: Write to buffer[0] (overwrite)
    Note over P: Write to buffer[0] (overwrite)
    C->>SM: read_idx = 1
    C->>SM: futex_wait(write_idx)
    Note over P: Write to buffer[1]
    P->>SM: write_idx = 1
    P->>SM: futex_wake(write_idx)
    Note over C: Reading buffer[0] (slow)
    
    Note over P,C: Second Consumer Cycle
    Note over P: Write to buffer[1] (overwrite)
    Note over P: Write to buffer[1] (overwrite)
    C->>SM: read_idx = 2
    C->>SM: futex_wait(write_idx)
    Note over P: Write to buffer[0]
    P->>SM: write_idx = 2
    P->>SM: futex_wake(write_idx)
    Note over C: Reading buffer[1] (slow)
    
    Note over P,C: Third Consumer Cycle
    Note over P: Write to buffer[0] (overwrite)
    Note over P: Write to buffer[0] (overwrite)
    C->>SM: read_idx = 1
    C->>SM: futex_wait(write_idx)
    Note over P: Write to buffer[1]
    P->>SM: write_idx = 1
    P->>SM: futex_wake(write_idx)
    Note over C: Reading buffer[0] (slow) 